---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, I'm Jay Boricha, a full-stack developer from India.
      <br />
      My primary tools of choice includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>React.Js</li>
        <li>Next.Js</li>
        <li>TypeScript</li>
        <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li>Node.Js</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about chess, cricket  and traveling.
      An hobby of mine is whatching chess streams, they're
      interesting and you get to learn a lot about the game.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
